user_prompt: Build a Python calculator package with: 1) A calc.py module with add, subtract, multiply, divide functions that handle edge cases (division by zero, type errors). 2) A build.sh shell script that runs chmod +x, creates a __init__.py, and echoes 'Build complete'. 3) A test_calc.py with pytest tests for all functions including edge cases. 4) Run the build.sh script. 5) Run pytest and show all test results.
